Job Details
Accounts Assistant – Logistics & Freight Forwarding – AED 4,500 pm
Responsibilities Posting journal entries and accruals and analysis of expenses accounts Reconciliation of GL accounts and preparing schedules of payment Preparation of monthly financial statements and MIS reports Assist with preparing final accounts Manage the petty cash receipts and payments
Skills & Experience Required 2 – 3 years’ experience in accounts / finance Knowledge of TALLY or Peachtree Good communication skills – fluency in English is essential
Education B Com in Finance or Accounting
To apply – please visit www.plumjobs.co and apply online
Telephone Number - +971 552 167567
Only candidates with relevant experience will be contacted within 2 days of their application
You can connect with us on LinkedIn and follow the Plum Jobs company page or follow us on Twitter and like us on Facebook
